text: Jenna Strauch (born 24 March 1997) is an Australian swimmer. She competed in the women's 200 metre breaststroke at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships. She reached the semi-finals and she did not qualify to compete in the final. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Australian female swimmers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
